---
/**
 * 404 page — bilingual, defaults to Japanese.
 * Astro serves this for all unmatched routes.
 */
---
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Page Not Found | 太旺旺株式会社</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --cream: #f7f2ea;
      --sumi: #1a1812;
      --kintya: #b8915c;
      --sumi-55: rgba(26, 24, 18, 0.55);
    }

    * { margin: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      background: var(--cream);
      color: var(--sumi);
      min-height: 100dvh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .error-page {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 400px;
    }

    .error-page__code {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 6rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--kintya);
      line-height: 1;
      margin-block-end: 1.5rem;
    }

    .error-page__title {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-block-end: 0.5rem;
    }

    .error-page__body {
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
      color: var(--sumi-55);
      margin-block-end: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .error-page__links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .error-page__links a {
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: var(--kintya);
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .error-page__links a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-underline-offset: 3px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="error-page">
    <p class="error-page__code">404</p>
    <h1 class="error-page__title">ページが見つかりません</h1>
    <p class="error-page__body">お探しのページは、移動または削除された可能性があります。</p>
    <div class="error-page__links">
      <a href="/ja/">トップページへ（日本語）</a>
      <a href="/zh/">回到首頁（中文）</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
